            "title": "Frugivorous bats as facilitators of natural regeneration in degraded habitats: A potential global tool",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Lays Cherobim",
                    "lastName": "Parolin"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
